OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cfor opening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FFormer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,7,FDonaldson returned to court today for
OL,8,Fthe first time in more than a year as
OL,9,Fa jury is set to be sworn in for the
OL,10,Fstart of his trial.
OL,12,FIt was a low-key and fast entrance
OL,13,Finto Newry Crown Court after he was
OL,14,Fdropped off by car.
OL,16,FThe waiting media, here from all over,
OL,17,Fand some onlookers, eager to catch a
OL,18,Fglimpse of the 63-year-old.
OL,20,FBut there was no-where near the number
OL,21,Fwhen he last appeared.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
