OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cfor opening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FPolice also here to make sure things
OL,7,Fran smoothly for what is the most high-
OL,8,Fprofile case before the courts in
OL,9,Frecent years.
OL,11,FThe former MP has been charged with
OL,12,Fand denies 18 alleged child sex
OL,13,Foffences allegedly involving two
OL,14,Fvictims.
OL,16,FThey include claims of rape, gross
OL,17,Findecency and indecent assault.
OL,19,FIt is alleged the offences were
OL,20,Fcommitted over a 20-year period
OL,21,Fbetween 1985 and 2008.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
