OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779894668
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cfor opening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FThe former MP's wife Lady Eleanor
OL,7,FDonaldson denies charges of aiding and
OL,8,Fabetting in her husband's alleged
OL,9,Foffences.
OL,11,FShe is not here and won't appear.
OL,13,FSince the couple were charged most of
OL,14,Fthe hearings have been centred on her
OL,15,Fill health.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
