CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779894668
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cfor opening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FLast week, after weighing up all the
OL,7,Fevidence, which included medical
OL,8,Freports submitted by the defence and
OL,9,Fprosecution, Judge Paul Ramsey ruled
OL,10,Fthe 60-year-old was unfit to stand
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,FHe opted, under the 1986 Mental Health
OL,14,FOrder, to hold a trial of the facts -
OL,15,Fwhich will run at the same as her
OL,16,Fhusband's.
OL,18,FBut the way it works is very different.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
