FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779894668
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cfor opening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FUnlike a normal trial, because someone
OL,7,Fhas been declared unfit on mental
OL,8,Fhealth grounds, a jury cannot find the
OL,9,Fperson guilty, instead they must
OL,10,Fdetermine if they have committed the
OL,11,Falleged act. They can also be
OL,12,Facquitted.
OL,14,FSentencing is also different - no
OL,15,Fprison - it is either a number of
OL,16,Ftreatment orders or absolute discharge.
OL,18,FLike a normal trial, the accused will
OL,19,Fbe represented by lawyers, but will
OL,20,Fnot play any part in proceedings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
