CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779894668
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cfor opening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FTo avoid any confusion. Sir Jeffrey
OL,7,FDonaldson is facing a normal criminal
OL,8,Ftrial.
OL,10,FIt is hoped jury selection will be
OL,11,Fcompleted today with the presentation
OL,12,Fof evidence to begin tomorrow.
OL,14,FBut that could always slide by a day
OL,15,For two.
OL,17,FIt is just over two years since the
OL,18,Fcouple first appeared in Newry Crown
OL,19,FCourt charged with historic child sex
OL,20,Foffences which they have always denied.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
